text:
Week Seven Football All Star Team Luke Feddersen IowaPreps.com Editor 
Iowa Preps has released our all star team from the seventh week of the football season. This includes athletes at a number of key positions and highlights the defenses that excelled as well. Subscribe today and never miss a thing!
